### 8. **AsyncProcessorConverterHelper - Sync-to-Async Bridge**
**File:** `/workspace/core/camel-support/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/support/AsyncProcessorConverterHelper.java`

**Purpose:** Converts synchronous Processor to AsyncProcessor

**Inner Class: ProcessorToAsyncProcessorBridge (Lines 49-169):**

```java
private static class ProcessorToAsyncProcessorBridge 
        implements DelegateProcessor, AsyncProcessor, Navigate<Processor>, Service {

    protected final Processor processor;

    @Override
    public boolean process(Exchange exchange, AsyncCallback callback) {
        if (processor == null) {
            callback.done(true);
            return true;
        }
        try {
            processor.process(exchange);  // Synchronous call
        } catch (Exception e) {
            exchange.setException(e);
        } finally {
            callback.done(true);  // Signal completion immediately
        }
        return true;  // Always synchronous
    }
}
```

**Static Methods:**
```java
public static AsyncProcessor convert(Processor value) {
    if (value instanceof AsyncProcessor asyncProcessor) {
        return asyncProcessor;
    }
    return new ProcessorToAsyncProcessorBridge(value);
}
```

**Pattern:** Wraps synchronous processors for uniform async handling; callback invoked synchronously

